      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power unit. This 3.2L straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal torque delivery. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission pairs with a factory limited-slip differential, providing a visceral, mechanical connection to the tarmac. Crucially, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced to ensure lateral stiffness and long-term chassis integrity. Suspension geometry remains true with upgraded bushings and refreshed dampers. This is a mechanically robust example for the purist who prioritizes throttle response and handling precision over a trailer-queen aesthetic.",
