      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2019 Lexus RX 350 is a prime example of a well-maintained luxury SUV, striking the perfect balance between daily utility and refined comfort. Finished in a deep Obsidian Black, the exterior maintains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains plush and inviting; while the driver\u2019s seat shows light natural creasing, the cabin is strictly non-smoker and free of stains or tears. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the intuitive climate control and premium audio system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, with a complete log of dealership maintenance records available for your review. The 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly, and the tires provide ample tread for the seasons ahead. This is an honest, reliable vehicle that has been treated with respect by its previous owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
